description: Nick is into extreme sports, working out, and girls.He caught our eye as he seemed to have the perfect next-door look to him. Nick has a bit of a reserved personality, but is wild when it comes to anything sexual. He says girls don't believe him when he tells them he needs a magnum condom... until he whips it out and shows them. Go easy on those girls, Nick... they just might get hurt with that thing.
title: Nick
